lead_paragraph: VfL Wolfsburg striker Bas Dost has recovered from a broken foot and will be in their squad for their Champions League quarter-final first leg against Real Madrid on Wednesday, coach Dieter Hecking said.

headline.print_headline: Fit-Again Dost in Wolfsburg Squad to Face Real
